SELECT
	scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city.scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__generic_territory_name AS scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__generic_territory_name,
	CAST(SUM(online_seconds) AS DOUBLE) / 3600.00 AS lspar_scaledops_minus_transport_rspar_dax_online_hours
FROM
	scaled_ops.f_driver_online_detail_h AS fact_data_source
LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT
		city_id AS scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id,
		max(generic_territory_name) AS scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__generic_territory_name
	FROM
		scaled_ops.v_grab_area_above_city
	GROUP BY
		1) AS scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city ON
	CAST(scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city.scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id__scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_scaled_ops_v_grab_area_above_city_city_id AS varchar)= CAST(city_id AS varchar)
WHERE
	DATE_TRUNC('day', STR_TO_DATE(CAST(date_id * 100 + hour_local AS VARCHAR), '%Y%m%d%H')) >= DATE_TRUNC('hour', STR_TO_DATE('2025-10-01 00:00:00', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%S'))
	AND DATE_TRUNC('day', STR_TO_DATE(CAST(date_id * 100 + hour_local AS VARCHAR), '%Y%m%d%H')) < DATE_TRUNC('hour', STR_TO_DATE('2025-10-30 00:00:00', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%S'))
	AND date_id >= 20250929
	AND date_id < 20251101
	AND (country_id = 4
		and business = 'Transport'
		and granularity = 'BUSINESS')
GROUP BY
	1
LIMIT 10001

table_meta.scaled_ops.mv_f_driver_online_detail_h_6:
CREATE MATERIALIZED VIEW `mv_f_driver_online_detail_h_6` (`date_id`, `city_id`, `country_id`, `business`, `business_x`, `granularity`, `hour_local`, `sum_in_transit_seconds`, `sum_online_seconds`, `sum_transit_seconds`, `sum_forced_idle_seconds`, `sum_idle_seconds`, `sum_fav_loc_online_seconds`, `sum_fav_loc_transit_seconds`, `driver_bitmap`)
COMMENT "MATERIALIZED_VIEW"
PARTITION BY (`date_id`)
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(`city_id`) BUCKETS 5 
ORDER BY (country_id)
REFRESH MANUAL
PROPERTIES (
"replicated_storage" = "true",
"replication_num" = "2",
"partition_refresh_number" = "1",
"compression" = "LZ4",
"datacache.enable" = "true",
"enable_async_write_back" = "false",
"storage_volume" = "default_volume",
"warehouse" = "default_warehouse"
)
AS SELECT `f_driver_online_detail_h`.`date_id`, `f_driver_online_detail_h`.`city_id`, `f_driver_online_detail_h`.`country_id`, `f_driver_online_detail_h`.`business`, CASE WHEN ((lower(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`business`)) IN ('grabexpress', 'express', 'logistics')) THEN 'Logistics' WHEN ((lower(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`business`)) IN ('grabkitchen', 'kitchen')) THEN 'Kitchen' WHEN ((lower(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`business`)) IN ('grabfood', 'food')) THEN 'Food' WHEN ((lower(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`business`)) IN ('grabmart', 'mart')) THEN 'Mart' WHEN ((lower(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`business`)) IN ('transport')) THEN 'Transport' ELSE `f_driver_online_detail_h`.`business` END AS `business_x`, `f_driver_online_detail_h`.`granularity`, `f_driver_online_detail_h`.`hour_local`, sum(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`in_transit_seconds`) AS `sum_in_transit_seconds`, sum(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`online_seconds`) AS `sum_online_seconds`, sum(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`transit_seconds`) AS `sum_transit_seconds`, sum(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`forced_idle_seconds`) AS `sum_forced_idle_seconds`, sum(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`idle_seconds`) AS `sum_idle_seconds`, sum(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`fav_loc_online_seconds`) AS `sum_fav_loc_online_seconds`, sum(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`fav_loc_transit_seconds`) AS `sum_fav_loc_transit_seconds`, ``.bitmap_agg(`f_driver_online_detail_h`.`driver_id`) AS `driver_bitmap`
FROM `scaled_ops`.`f_driver_online_detail_h`
WHERE `f_driver_online_detail_h`.`granularity` = 'BUSINESS'
GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7;

view_meta.scaled_ops.v_grab_area_above_city:
WITH `c` (`city_id`, `purposes`, `parent_territory`, `parent_region`) AS (SELECT `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`city_id`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`purposes`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`parent_territory`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`parent_region`
FROM `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`
WHERE (`ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`layer` = 'City') AND (`ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`purposes` = 'Generic')) , `t` (`area_id`, `area_name`, `purposes`, `layer`) AS (SELECT `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`area_id`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`area_name`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`purposes`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`layer`
FROM `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`
WHERE (`ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`layer` = 'Territory') AND (`ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`purposes` = 'Generic')) , `r` (`area_id`, `area_name`, `purposes`, `layer`) AS (SELECT `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`area_id`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`area_name`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`purposes`, `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`layer`
FROM `ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`
WHERE (`ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`layer` = 'Region') AND (`ff_de`.`d_grab_area_summary`.`purposes` = 'Generic')) SELECT `c`.`city_id`, max(CASE WHEN (`t`.`layer` = 'Territory') THEN `t`.`area_id` ELSE NULL END) AS `generic_territory_id`, max(CASE WHEN (`t`.`layer` = 'Territory') THEN `t`.`area_name` ELSE NULL END) AS `generic_territory_name`, max(CASE WHEN (`r`.`layer` = 'Region') THEN `r`.`area_id` ELSE NULL END) AS `generic_region_id`, max(CASE WHEN (`r`.`layer` = 'Region') THEN `r`.`area_name` ELSE NULL END) AS `generic_region_name`
FROM `c` LEFT OUTER JOIN `t` ON (`c`.`parent_territory` = `t`.`area_name`) AND (`c`.`purposes` = `t`.`purposes`) LEFT OUTER JOIN `r` ON (`c`.`parent_region` = `r`.`area_name`) AND (`c`.`purposes` = `r`.`purposes`)
GROUP BY 1
